graph LR
    LlamaOperator[Llama Stack K8s Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    LlamaOperator -->|container platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.20+]
    LlamaOperator -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19.4]
    LlamaOperator -->|manifest templating| Kustomize[kustomize kyaml v0.18.1]
    LlamaOperator -->|inference backend| InferenceProviders[Inference Providers<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI/Bedrock]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    LlamaOperator -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    LlamaOperator -.->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    LlamaOperator -->|cluster monitoring| OSMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor CRD]
    LlamaOperator -->|pod security| SCC[Security Context Constraints<br/>anyuid SCC]

    %% External Services
    LlamaOperator -->|image storage| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>docker.io, quay.io]
    InferenceProviders -->|model weights| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>huggingface.co]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| LlamaOperator
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|automated deployment| LlamaOperator
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|API calls| LlamaOperator

    %% Managed Resources
    LlamaOperator -->|creates/manages| ManagedResources[Deployments<br/>Services<br/>PVCs<br/>NetworkPolicies<br/>Ingresses]

